sentences: Neil Andrew Carter (born 11 May 1958) is an English musician who has worked in diverse genres throughout his career.
2010 saw an unexpected return to rock with Gary Moore, playing festivals across Europe and a tour of Ukraine and Russia.
Future tours and a Celtic rock album were to follow but this was curtailed by the death of Gary Moore in February 2011.

On 30 April 2019, it was announced that he would return to UFO for their 'Last Orders' tour, following the death of Paul Raymond with Neil replacing Paul.
The tour began in June 2019 in Germany with concerts and festival appearances.
It is expected that following the USA dates in autumn 2019 there will be some concerts in 2020 as a continuation of the bands’ final 50th anniversary tour.

Neil left Brighton College in June 2014 to move down to his home in Lanzarote.
